Third-party software:

This product depends on software distributed under separate, compatible
open-source licenses. Each dependency retains its own license; see the
respective package metadata under node_modules/ for details. A consolidated
attribution list is generated for distributed builds (see the application's
"Open source licenses" screen).

Corral integrates with third-party AI providers, trackers, and repositories
using credentials supplied by the user (BYOK). Corral does not bundle any
proprietary provider binary, and does not embed any provider credentials.
Compliance with each provider's terms of service is the user's responsibility.
